      "text": "[[WyCash Plus]] was growing faster than we could keep in our heads. [[Gary Goldberg]] was working out formulas from careful reading of contracts while I was implementing those formulas where they went in the system. Eventually it dawned on me: Load the spreadsheet data into the program and let it check itself."
